Americans have a new “smart weapon.”
The US military has sent a new “smart” weapon to Afghnistan, known only as the XM-25 code.
The generals believe that this new automatic rifle will influence the conflict there with the Taliban and “will change the game” for their benefit.
The new weapon is like a super-accurate cannon
